profile: We specialize in outdoor projects, decks, outdoor kitchens, gazebos etc. We have been in business for 10 years and also have a retail store. One of our specialties is tropical themed backyard projects, tiki bars, palapas, faux palm trees, and much more. Our website is www.tikiescapes.com We also do full renovations including additions and basements.
